  <p><b><span id="Service_Portfolio_Manager">Service Portfolio Manager - Process Owner</span></b> </p>
  <ul>
    <li>The Service Portfolio Manager decides on a strategy to serve customers in cooperation with the IT Steering Group, and develops the service provider's offerings and capabilities.</li>
  </ul>
  <p><br />
  </p>
  <p><b><span id="IT_Steering_Group">IT Steering Group (ISG)</span></b> </p>
  <ul>
    <li>The IT Steering Group (ISG) sets the direction and strategy for IT Services. It includes members of senior management from business and IT. The IT Steering Group reviews the business and IT strategies in order to make sure that they are aligned. It also sets priorities of service development programs/ projects.</li>
  </ul>
